{
  "stem": "15943.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, my mother and my aunt when they were there, when we first moved-- when they moved in with us, because we were at-- in our place and they moved in with us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother and my aunt used to do the cooking, take the rations that came in and divide it and tried to improvise and make it sound like this is a fancy cake you're eating, which was something from the coffee grinds.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They made a cake, but they called it a babka.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And yeah, they gave it real, real nice names, make it appetizing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or the skins of potatoes-- and they would-- well, now we know that it's healthy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, [LAUGHS] we didn't think about healthy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It just was food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they would make cakes out of it and delicacies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, the, the, the women were very ingenious and improvising with whatever, with whatever they could.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they did the cooking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Later, when everybody had to go to factories, there was nothing to cook.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The main meal was the bowl of soup in the factory and whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We would get some bread or sometimes some margarine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Or whatever the rations, we kind of divided them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There really wasn't, wasn't much to cook.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she didn't have much to sell because whatever was of value, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gruber took it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was nothin' to sell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brother said one time-- when my mother was taken away and I became their legal guardian, my brother sold their bread-- that was the valuable possession-- at one point to get vitamins for me-- [NON-ENGLISH], that was the name of the vitamins-- because my legs-- the, the loss of-- from malnutrition, the loss of calcium, I couldn't stand up.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I looked swollen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I looked like I was fat.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
